link_title: YOU WONT BELIEVE THIS IS ACCRA GHANA | REAL LIFE OF LOCAL GHANAIANS LIVING IN GHANA
description: #ACCRAGHANA #LIFEINGHANA #LIVINGINGHANA #GHANA  #ghanatouristattractions I explored a township within the Accra region of Ghana called Teshie. Its an interesting area to visit as there is such a big contrast between Teshie and the main parts of Accra. In this part of Ghana, most of the people still practice their traditions and culture. They still have a chief, a priest and a shrine.  This area is a high crime area but can serve as a great tourist site given that its so accessible within Accra, there is so much culture to learn and is generally safe during the day.
